Package: libarchengine-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Priority: extra
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: ArchEngine Database Libraries [development]
 This is the development package which contains headers and static
 libraries for the ArchEngine database library.

Package: libarchengine
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
	 ${misc:Depends}
Description: ArchEngine Database Libraries [runtime]
 This is the runtime package for programs that use the ArchEngine
 database library.

